column5: Has anybody fished below the Ear Falls Dam this fall? We have been there in the past and have had some great fishing there. Mike Kansas
Jiggerster fishes below the dam, if memory serves me! Maybe a search is in order!?
Fished below the dam on sunday morning for an hour from shore. Limit of 17 to 18 inchers. Put back 6 or 7 bigger ones.
